{"lang":"zh","stage":6,"title":"longer everyday sentences","sentences":[{"t":"我去派对了。","en":"I went to the party.","r":"Wǒ qù pàiduì le.","a":"n_46d12ec1bd4b.mp3"},{"t":"你来派对吗？","en":"Are you coming to the party?","r":"Nǐ lái pàiduì ma?","a":"n_235dc5c79067.mp3"},{"t":"公交现在来了。","en":"The bus is coming now.","r":"Gōngjiāo xiànzài lái le.","a":"n_af80665b0a2b.mp3"},{"t":"我住在这附近。","en":"I live close to here.","r":"Wǒ zhù zài zhè fùjìn.","a":"n_8f8dbaebd8d5.mp3"},{"t":"他谁都认识。","en":"He knows everyone.","r":"Tā shéi dōu rènshi.","a":"n_a6e05eeb3959.mp3"},{"t":"我头疼。","en":"My head hurts.","r":"Wǒ tóu téng.","a":"n_353b7fab0c20.mp3"},{"t":"五分钟就到。","en":"It arrives in five minutes.","r":"Wǔ fēnzhōng jiù dào.","a":"n_9d722e809d32.mp3"},{"t":"你应该说实话。","en":"You should tell the truth.","r":"Nǐ yīnggāi shuō shíhuà.","a":"n_aff1b344db0f.mp3"},{"t":"你应该休息一下。","en":"You should rest a little.","r":"Nǐ yīnggāi xiūxi yíxià.","a":"n_4841196b0e52.mp3"},{"t":"这个太好吃了。","en":"This is delicious.","r":"Zhège tài hǎochī le.","a":"n_ed76e92b24c8.mp3"},{"t":"我等不下去了。","en":"I can't wait any longer.","r":"Wǒ děng bu xiàqù le.","a":"n_f1620894203c.mp3"},{"t":"我想看看会怎样。","en":"I want to see what happens.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng kànkan huì zěnyàng.","a":"n_0a5240b76fd9.mp3"},{"t":"我一个小时就回来。","en":"I'll be back in an hour.","r":"Wǒ yí ge xiǎoshí jiù huílái.","a":"n_b13267835e2f.mp3"},{"t":"我想喝点东西。","en":"I want something to drink.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng hē diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_bcba6d341a9c.mp3"},{"t":"你想喝点什么？","en":"What are you going to drink?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng hē diǎn shénme?","a":"n_b2d0d6ea6fbf.mp3"},{"t":"我喝水就行。","en":"I'll have water.","r":"Wǒ hē shuǐ jiù xíng.","a":"n_81c41d8b6e25.mp3"},{"t":"这次我请。","en":"This time I'm paying.","r":"Zhè cì wǒ qǐng.","a":"n_0647f265de19.mp3"},{"t":"在右边。","en":"It's on the right.","r":"Zài yòubiān.","a":"n_851102a165db.mp3"},{"t":"往右拐。","en":"Turn right.","r":"Wǎng yòu guǎi.","a":"n_9a19c723642d.mp3"},{"t":"还是坐出租车吧。","en":"Better go by taxi.","r":"Háishi zuò chūzūchē ba.","a":"n_4dba1d8502fd.mp3"},{"t":"她是我朋友。","en":"She's my friend.","r":"Tā shì wǒ péngyou.","a":"n_3f74572b25e7.mp3"},{"t":"她是你朋友吗？","en":"Is she your friend?","r":"Tā shì nǐ péngyou ma?","a":"n_83daaa4708ac.mp3"},{"t":"这是我朋友。","en":"This is my friend.","r":"Zhè shì wǒ péngyou.","a":"n_a392593f964e.mp3"},{"t":"终于到星期五了。","en":"It's finally Friday.","r":"Zhōngyú dào xīngqīwǔ le.","a":"n_674384c75d2f.mp3"},{"t":"见到你我很开心。","en":"I'm happy to see you.","r":"Jiàndào nǐ wǒ hěn kāixīn.","a":"n_961f8317042d.mp3"},{"t":"我待会儿来看你。","en":"I'm coming to see you later.","r":"Wǒ dāihuìr lái kàn nǐ.","a":"n_78c667b3724f.mp3"},{"t":"她有一只猫。","en":"She has a cat.","r":"Tā yǒu yì zhī māo.","a":"n_239d3fe93cba.mp3"},{"t":"我宁愿待在家里。","en":"I'd rather stay home.","r":"Wǒ nìngyuàn dāi zài jiā lǐ.","a":"n_8469d3d150ba.mp3"},{"t":"我们要迟到了。","en":"We're going to be late.","r":"Wǒmen yào chídào le.","a":"n_c4431ddcdd7f.mp3"},{"t":"你能帮我个忙吗？","en":"Can you do me a favor?","r":"Nǐ néng bāng wǒ ge máng ma?","a":"n_34797bfc690a.mp3"},{"t":"这儿有什么好吃的？","en":"What's good here?","r":"Zhèr yǒu shénme hǎochī de?","a":"n_85ec3380b43d.mp3"},{"t":"往好的方面想。","en":"Look on the bright side.","r":"Wǎng hǎo de fāngmiàn xiǎng.","a":"n_40bc19d13a24.mp3"},{"t":"给我一个好理由。","en":"Give me one good reason.","r":"Gěi wǒ yí ge hǎo lǐyóu.","a":"n_8aea75cd067c.mp3"},{"t":"这个更简单。","en":"This is easier.","r":"Zhège gèng jiǎndān.","a":"n_3194cf2bf8e4.mp3"},{"t":"以前更简单。","en":"It used to be easier.","r":"Yǐqián gèng jiǎndān.","a":"n_2636a31c220b.mp3"},{"t":"在左边。","en":"It's on the left.","r":"Zài zuǒbiān.","a":"n_14c7d8ab1970.mp3"},{"t":"往左拐。","en":"Turn left.","r":"Wǎng zuǒ guǎi.","a":"n_4406b19f31f2.mp3"},{"t":"我去车站。","en":"I'm going to the station.","r":"Wǒ qù chēzhàn.","a":"n_d08573764f20.mp3"},{"t":"车站在哪儿？","en":"Where is the station?","r":"Chēzhàn zài nǎr?","a":"n_5529fd433e23.mp3"},{"t":"我昨天吃了点好吃的。","en":"I ate something tasty yesterday.","r":"Wǒ zuótiān chī le diǎn hǎochī de.","a":"n_cee079fe559a.mp3"},{"t":"我准备好开始了。","en":"I'm ready to start.","r":"Wǒ zhǔnbèi hǎo kāishǐ le.","a":"n_6e04e46dfc53.mp3"},{"t":"我会做一点饭。","en":"I know how to cook a little.","r":"Wǒ huì zuò yìdiǎn fàn.","a":"n_f64ee07b5358.mp3"},{"t":"没人想买那个。","en":"Nobody wants to buy that.","r":"Méi rén xiǎng mǎi nàge.","a":"n_b96af22c4b8a.mp3"},{"t":"你欠我五欧元。","en":"You owe me five euros.","r":"Nǐ qiàn wǒ wǔ ōuyuán.","a":"n_d834425472fc.mp3"},{"t":"我很熟这条路。","en":"I know the way well.","r":"Wǒ hěn shú zhè tiáo lù.","a":"n_7572183fade6.mp3"},{"t":"我今晚不出去。","en":"I'm not going out tonight.","r":"Wǒ jīnwǎn bù chūqù.","a":"n_e5a4164f64ce.mp3"},{"t":"我能问一件事吗？","en":"Can I ask one thing?","r":"Wǒ néng wèn yí jiàn shì ma?","a":"n_bb5e088ac042.mp3"},{"t":"这事我怎么跟你说呢？","en":"How do I tell you this?","r":"Zhè shì wǒ zěnme gēn nǐ shuō ne?","a":"n_5f65a7a8a4b5.mp3"},{"t":"我现在该怎么跟他说？","en":"What do I tell him now?","r":"Wǒ xiànzài gāi zěnme gēn tā shuō?","a":"n_775d5d7b5088.mp3"},{"t":"他知道答案。","en":"He knows the answer.","r":"Tā zhīdào dá'àn.","a":"n_9821dfbe4e04.mp3"},{"t":"我谢过她了。","en":"I thanked her.","r":"Wǒ xiè guò tā le.","a":"n_d2be69c02159.mp3"},{"t":"我们还没准备好。","en":"We're not ready yet.","r":"Wǒmen hái méi zhǔnbèi hǎo.","a":"n_2758e33de0e6.mp3"},{"t":"我需要时间想想。","en":"I need time to think.","r":"Wǒ xūyào shíjiān xiǎngxiang.","a":"n_47c9f08520ab.mp3"},{"t":"我家很小。","en":"My house is small.","r":"Wǒ jiā hěn xiǎo.","a":"n_4cf796b064ac.mp3"},{"t":"我们家很小。","en":"We have a small house.","r":"Wǒmen jiā hěn xiǎo.","a":"n_aa19e2f74ab8.mp3"},{"t":"我喜欢这首歌。","en":"I like this song.","r":"Wǒ xǐhuan zhè shǒu gē.","a":"n_edff8ec0231b.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都没说。","en":"I didn't say anything.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu méi shuō.","a":"n_62ddd57dea84.mp3"},{"t":"我已经知道怎么用了。","en":"I already know how it works.","r":"Wǒ yǐjīng zhīdào zěnme yòng le.","a":"n_52f407c8231a.mp3"},{"t":"她起得很早。","en":"She gets up early.","r":"Tā qǐ de hěn zǎo.","a":"n_f16eb54abdf6.mp3"},{"t":"你有什么喝的？","en":"What do you have to drink?","r":"Nǐ yǒu shénme hē de?","a":"n_5a3523d3169f.mp3"},{"t":"能再给我点面包吗？","en":"Can you bring me more bread?","r":"Néng zài gěi wǒ diǎn miànbāo ma?","a":"n_dabf1417a76a.mp3"},{"t":"她住在家里。","en":"She lives at home.","r":"Tā zhù zài jiā lǐ.","a":"n_2250e2406086.mp3"},{"t":"我工作到六点。","en":"I work until six.","r":"Wǒ gōngzuò dào liù diǎn.","a":"n_aae554e7b0bd.mp3"},{"t":"我想卖掉我的手机。","en":"I want to sell my phone.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng màidiào wǒ de shǒujī.","a":"n_dd8554dfc68c.mp3"},{"t":"我在哪儿买票？","en":"Where do I buy the ticket?","r":"Wǒ zài nǎr mǎi piào?","a":"n_ba797813a086.mp3"},{"t":"我嗓子疼。","en":"My throat hurts.","r":"Wǒ sǎngzi téng.","a":"n_f666be2a9abc.mp3"},{"t":"他是我的一个朋友。","en":"He's a friend of mine.","r":"Tā shì wǒ de yí ge péngyou.","a":"n_b0f807d78f89.mp3"},{"t":"这是我的荣幸。","en":"The pleasure is mine.","r":"Zhè shì wǒ de róngxìng.","a":"n_1d09595cf308.mp3"},{"t":"我今天特别忙。","en":"I'm really busy today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān tèbié máng.","a":"n_bf1e148946b9.mp3"},{"t":"我朋友们都很开心。","en":"My friends are happy.","r":"Wǒ péngyoumen dōu hěn kāixīn.","a":"n_d5d449b379b6.mp3"},{"t":"要走了我很舍不得。","en":"I'm sad to leave.","r":"Yào zǒu le wǒ hěn shěbude.","a":"n_18ca1024c60a.mp3"},{"t":"我几乎从不早到。","en":"I almost never arrive early.","r":"Wǒ jīhū cóng bù zǎo dào.","a":"n_89de96be9a70.mp3"},{"t":"我们现在得吃点东西。","en":"We need to eat something now.","r":"Wǒmen xiànzài děi chī diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_4beee4fdadab.mp3"},{"t":"我超爱巧克力。","en":"I love chocolate.","r":"Wǒ chāo ài qiǎokèlì.","a":"n_4b40e484194d.mp3"},{"t":"我喜欢晒太阳。","en":"I like the sun.","r":"Wǒ xǐhuan shài tàiyáng.","a":"n_793ec4147b15.mp3"},{"t":"你喜欢咖啡还是茶？","en":"Do you prefer coffee or tea?","r":"Nǐ xǐhuan kāfēi háishi chá?","a":"n_ee215e498966.mp3"},{"t":"希望能早点见到你。","en":"I'd like to see you soon.","r":"Xīwàng néng zǎodiǎn jiàndào nǐ.","a":"n_550843f92e9a.mp3"},{"t":"我现在没法跟你说。","en":"I can't tell you now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài méi fǎ gēn nǐ shuō.","a":"n_29d6fe82627d.mp3"},{"t":"我今天到得特别早。","en":"I got here really early today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān dào de tèbié zǎo.","a":"n_6cbf8accbe0b.mp3"},{"t":"她跟我们一起来。","en":"She's coming with us.","r":"Tā gēn wǒmen yìqǐ lái.","a":"n_a7ec23b194e7.mp3"},{"t":"我们五分钟后出发。","en":"We're leaving in five minutes.","r":"Wǒmen wǔ fēnzhōng hòu chūfā.","a":"n_19166df72a6b.mp3"},{"t":"你作业写完了吗？","en":"Did you do the homework yet?","r":"Nǐ zuòyè xiě wán le ma?","a":"n_22cc20d3cb1a.mp3"},{"t":"你为什么问那么多？","en":"Why do you ask so much?","r":"Nǐ wèishénme wèn nàme duō?","a":"n_4349f120a505.mp3"},{"t":"他问好多问题。","en":"He asks a lot of questions.","r":"Tā wèn hǎoduō wèntí.","a":"n_7fe86ca60afb.mp3"},{"t":"我不想跟任何人说。","en":"I don't want to tell anyone anything.","r":"Wǒ bù xiǎng gēn rènhé rén shuō.","a":"n_532b613b9eed.mp3"},{"t":"下午见。","en":"See you this afternoon.","r":"Xiàwǔ jiàn.","a":"n_935d5e0872cc.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道他叫什么。","en":"I don't know his name.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào tā jiào shénme.","a":"n_658d4c109c76.mp3"},{"t":"她知道我的故事。","en":"She knows my story.","r":"Tā zhīdào wǒ de gùshi.","a":"n_adac8934b0c1.mp3"},{"t":"我手疼。","en":"My hand hurts.","r":"Wǒ shǒu téng.","a":"n_91e05879728d.mp3"},{"t":"我把号码给你。","en":"I'll give you my number.","r":"Wǒ bǎ hàomǎ gěi nǐ.","a":"n_2facb1a0ae8e.mp3"},{"t":"教我一下怎么做。","en":"Show me how it's done.","r":"Jiāo wǒ yíxià zěnme zuò.","a":"n_706fbfc6c356.mp3"},{"t":"我跟你保证过的。","en":"I gave you my word.","r":"Wǒ gēn nǐ bǎozhèng guò de.","a":"n_027bec66c6be.mp3"},{"t":"能给我点吗？","en":"Will you give me some?","r":"Néng gěi wǒ diǎn ma?","a":"n_657aed62d5b6.mp3"},{"t":"你看到他怎么看我的吗？","en":"Did you see how he looked at me?","r":"Nǐ kàndào tā zěnme kàn wǒ de ma?","a":"n_0803fc4f4088.mp3"}]}